    "name": "破碎怪谈：切勿直视",
    "steam_appid": 2351330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《破碎怪谈：切勿直视》</strong>是错综复杂的 <i>破碎怪谈</i> 系列的第一人称心理恐怖游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/21b086640b7e55152facc5e07615d229.poster.avif?t=1763608943\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/21b086640b7e55152facc5e07615d229.webm?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/21b086640b7e55152facc5e07615d229.mp4?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真嗣是一名年轻的“家里蹲”青年，生存在东京的一间狭小公寓里。但由于拖欠房租、账单堆积如山，再加上家人的不理解，他感到与世隔绝——甚至连自己都对自己感到陌生。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/e812a9e978ae1f341bef6ea3ee5eb186.poster.avif?t=1763608943\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/e812a9e978ae1f341bef6ea3ee5eb186.webm?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/e812a9e978ae1f341bef6ea3ee5eb186.mp4?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他唯一的逃避方式便是玩游戏，但即便如此，也无法缓解他心中沉重的焦虑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/878d9532e1154d8b2ba6c4339571f331.poster.avif?t=1763608943\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/878d9532e1154d8b2ba6c4339571f331.webm?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/878d9532e1154d8b2ba6c4339571f331.mp4?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将探索真嗣逐渐崩溃的内心世界，但请务必小心。百目鬼（Hyakume），一个有着百眼的邪恶实体，正在暗中窥视，等待着合适的时机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/47345facfb6b9fcadc5139e4fe0f1318.poster.avif?t=1763608943\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/47345facfb6b9fcadc5139e4fe0f1318.webm?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/47345facfb6b9fcadc5139e4fe0f1318.mp4?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的笔记本电脑是连接外界的唯一途径。但请注意，安全或许也只是一个假象…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/7633da346b6db696373d8b7c89496ea2.poster.avif?t=1763608943\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/7633da346b6db696373d8b7c89496ea2.webm?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351330/extras/7633da346b6db696373d8b7c89496ea2.mp4?t=1763608943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
